metadata.description:
NFT GoPass has created a Top-Tier Security Protocol for pe3qing into and validating offline cold storage hardware wallets in real time. 

This service requires no custodializing of security keys, no connecting your hardware wallet to to a website and only requests your minting and/or public wallet address. 

Real time cold storage asset validation can be accomplished when following our simple guide beginning with the minting of 2 or more of our NFT Parity security tokens.

For help, support and more information, please contact us at NFTGoPass.io

Parity Token Process - Patent Pending - April 2023
